AUDIO: 'Are you looking for a free open-source [music] alternative to RabbitMQ or Kafka that\'s simpler to run and faster out of the box? Let\'s discover NATS, a lightweight, high-performance messaging system built for modern distributed'

[00:12] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'applications. It handles pub/sub, request-reply, and persistent streaming all through a single binary with sub-millisecond latency and supports clients in Go, Rust, Python, JavaScript,'

